column5: Alarm was set for 8:30 to get ready for fishing today at 11:30, but I am awake now
Been up since 3 with a sick kid, alternating OFC with cleaning up vomit, smells like catfish bait or maybe I'm just dreaming of soft water. No fishing today.
Ummmmmm..................OK.............my life right now is much simpler. Hope all works out jughead and your kid gets better.
Good morning tjsa good luck on your fishing trip  Rob
Good morning Tom, and all...I decided to sleep in today, Good luck today Tom, and the rest of ya's behave yourselves  Maureen

Mornin, gang!  Slept waaay in, and was just thinking about doing some holiday geocaching when my leash rang.  Just flying through for my morning OFC fix before that service call.  Sick kid = catfish bait = happy daydreaming?  Gotta love a hobby that makes that dirty job more pleasant.  Hope the fish are biting, tjsa!
